# Wallet private key for deploying contracts to Kite Testnet
# IMPORTANT:
#   - This is your wallet's private key (export from MetaMask: Account Details > Show Private Key)
#   - NEVER commit the real .env file (already in .gitignore)
#   - Use a fresh wallet you only use for testnet, NOT your main wallet
#   - Fund this wallet at https://faucet.gokite.ai before deploying
AGENT_PRIVATE_KEY=0xYourPrivateKeyHere
